Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:06.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Can you hear this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's hoarse from yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:25.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Until your heart can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:34.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and sun high-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not here to make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,even what I'm looking for can't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowing, be honest with yourself and smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,because when two people lay close, time overlaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:07.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:28.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only wizards who have been given permission by the master can take on S class quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:34.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess they'd be impossible for Natsu or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, not in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:39.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, one of the requests on the second floor has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An S class quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.83,0:02:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what? A request is gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was put up on the second floor, then it's an S class, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would be stupid enough to take something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.66,0:02:56.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a cat with wings tear one off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.50,0:03:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means it's Natsu and Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Going out on an S class quest without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought they were dumb, but not {\i1}that{\i0} dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a serious violation of the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:17.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they make it back they're expelled... Right, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with their skills they won't be coming back from an S class, will they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:26.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, if you knew, why didn't you stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:31.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All I saw was a cat burglar run off with a scrap of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea that was actually Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:39.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I never would have thought Natsu would go on an S class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Been a while since I've seen you look at me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which request is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:49.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The cursed island, Galuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Galuna Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:53.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are such idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus! Go bring them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:01.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:05.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't the wizards in this guild supposed to be able to take care of themselves? {He's taunting his grandfather}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who other than you in here has the power to bring Natsu back by force?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps... {You had "Pops" Didn't we go for Gramps a few episodes back?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that one ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cursed Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The port town of Hargeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:30.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, how nostalgic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This was the town where we all met, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nostalgic? It wasn't exactly that long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's like an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:42.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, first thing is to find a ship to take us to Galuna Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:44.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're swimming, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:48.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's even less a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Galuna Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:52.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:53.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going anywhere near it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:56.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me break! I don't want to hear the name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:59.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't mention that island around this port.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cursed, and it's a bad omen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:08.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you want to go there, but there isn't any ship here that'll take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:10.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even pirates avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided. We're swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:17.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:22.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from Gramps to bring you back. {replaced fom Pops}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The jig's up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go back now, you might even get away without being expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:28.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:29.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:32.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if! I'm goin' on an S class quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't got the skills to handle it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Erza finds out about this, you'll... {Changed from Elza -- if that got resolved, let me know}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two forced me to come with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:47.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna face Erza down! {Changed from Elza}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:49.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna back down from this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a direct order from the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring you back by force if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:56.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain if you get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you wizards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.43,0:06:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be here to lift the curse from the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:06.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:08.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:12.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:18.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, guess we're ridin' this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking Gray with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this guy goes back to the guild, Erza'll be coming next! {Changed from Elza}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, {\i1}now{\i0} I get scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to talk, after getting me mixed up in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you launch the boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Bobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:43.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I once was a citizen of that island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away from that cursed isle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:54.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you go to that island, grave misfortune will befall you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really undo the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:05.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mister, your arm...  {also considered "dude" but took me out of character a bit}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:08.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The curse... You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Galuna Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? There's something shining on the peak of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he fall overboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared when we weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a giant wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're being engulfed! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, grab onto the boat and fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:45.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Galuna Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:06.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A giant wave washed us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing we lucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:13.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But what was with that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something about the Demon Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares! Let's go exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an expedition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:23.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're more interested in that than the request?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:27.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There seems to be only one village on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chieftain there is the person who made the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:40.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The ship's destroyed, so you can't bring us back. {what happened to swimming? :) }
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:50.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be annoying if you got up to the second floor before me, and if you got expelled that wouldn't be any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:55.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We do this job right, and Gramps has nothing to complain about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:06.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep Out. {This wins the "unneccesary subtitle" award!}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:09.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we made it here. Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:12.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they mean, "keep out?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us! Please open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:19.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we bust it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:21.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.25,0:09:26.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're from the wizard's guild, Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't hear that anyone accepted the request!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:32.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There must have been a mix up, and the message was late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.23,0:09:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us your marks! All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.85,0:09:39.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They actually came!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're entering the mouth of a giant monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the chief of this village, Moka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Firstly, I have something to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.01,0:10:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as the man on the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:06.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those sideburns are incredible! {I love the "awesome!" but it doesn't match the visual where he's got a shocked face}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no... This is what I wanted to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:18.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Every living thing on this island has been cursed like this. Dogs and birds, without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I doubt you, but what basis do you have for calling it a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you considered it might be an epidemic?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've consulted countless doctors, but they say there is no disease like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:37.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this appearance of ours is linked to moon's evil spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:38.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon's spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:47.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This place has absorbed moonlight since ancient times, and the island once sparkled beautifully like the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:54.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But some years ago, the light from the moon started changing to a purple color.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.41,0:10:56.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A purple moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon is coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! The moon is purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That really gives me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:13.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the evil spell of the moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.67,0:11:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for startling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:42.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! You got horns and spines and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:53.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I get some?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He thinks this is cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's ever said that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:12:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's a real problem for them to look like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.62,0:12:04.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad. Guess we'd better do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:05.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.89,0:12:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a clue, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Returning to the matter at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:16.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the purple moon appears, we all change to these demonic forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If this cannot be called a curse, then what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:27.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When the morning comes, everyone returns to their previous forms,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,however some never change back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their very minds have been stolen from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:39.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who have been turned into demons, who have lost their minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:42.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there might be a way to return them to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:48.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave them be, then everyone would be killed by the demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we lock them up, they destroy the jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed my own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:03.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My son, whose mind was turned into that of a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But yesterday, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:12.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! I know why that guy disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.70,0:13:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't rest in peace, could he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please save this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:26.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If things stay like this, all of us will lose our minds and turn to demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:27.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:30.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:36.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one way to rid us of the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.18,0:13:37.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please destroy the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon just keeps getting creepier the more you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:49.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, hurry and close the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The chief explained, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get exposed to too much moonlight, we'll turn into demons ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:13:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they seriously expect us to destroy the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows how many punches it'll take? {I see "hits" and I think "hit points"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning on destroying it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't think there's a wizard that could actually do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:12.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But "destroy the moon" is the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we accept a request and can't complete it, it'll look bad for Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do the impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did you plan on getting to the moon anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:30.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he said to destroy the moon, but if we poke around maybe we can find another way to lift the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:34.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking all day after the shipwreck... I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.27,0:14:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you stripping?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! So tomorrow we go exploring the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:39.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll think about it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:46.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm tired, too. Let's go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.29,0:14:55.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to sleep between a beast and an exhibitionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's early...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really damn early...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault I couldn't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get motivated and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'kay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Clock, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Horologium!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is 7:48.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:25.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think we can really lift the curse without destroying the moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:27.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well what other choice do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:31.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if we could destroy it, it's a bad idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't have the moon-viewing festival anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:38.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true! We'd never eat the limited-time-only "Fairy Tail Moon-View Steak" again? {First, I like "would be no more" but not for Natsu's character. Next, I don't think "Tsukimi" is self-explanitor at all. I wish it were, but...} {do you think that a note explaining "tsukimi" is necessary or obvious from context?}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'd do if my favorite Moon-View Salted Fish was gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:46.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey you two! I don't know what you're blabbing about, but keep it down, will you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:50.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:54.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you really use Celestial Spirits like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:57.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against a curse here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary when it's something ephemeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I call an S class quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:08.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll freeze that curse up no prob! Nothing to be scared of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"You guys really are idiots" she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:28.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hurry up and get it, guys!" she says. {I know that Lucy doesn't know that Angellica is female, but it's best not to put the idea in the viewer's minds where there is a choice}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:39.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, when did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:49.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!" they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eww!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A mouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a strong sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:03.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do that from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:19.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's some kind of building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go in there while we have the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat it up while we have the chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:33.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Temple of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite large.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:37.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What era is this thing from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:41.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.18,0:17:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The island was originally called "The Island of the Moon."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Island of the Moon, the moon's curse, moon symbols...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These ruins are really suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're in horrible shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this floor even safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, you idiot! Look what you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:12.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:17.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you think before destroying things, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.21,0:18:19.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, can you fly up with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Underground ruins, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here and all, so let's go exploring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough running amuck out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:36.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:39.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliora!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking... Why is Deliora here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it'd be in a place like this! {The ice is a she, but I would call the demon an "it," unless it's a part of the speaker's characterization. But Gray would never dignify it with a gender assignment. It murdered his parents}{editor: does deliora have a sex?  should I use "she"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.51,0:19:28.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon of Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon of The Ashtray?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like it was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard people's voices around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:49.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's noon, I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Toby, you got exposed to the Moon Drip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got like, ears and stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No dude! They're like, fashion, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just teasing, you dolt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yûka, you're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:04.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon Drip?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they talking about the curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.15,0:20:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yûka-san, Toby-san, I bring sad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you, Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica has been bullied by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mouse, dude! Don't give it no fancy name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:22.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She is not a mouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:26.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica is a hunter that runs through the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:29.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And... love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got some {\i1}serious{\i0} weirdos here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:33.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not from this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They smell different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And they don't seem like they're cursed either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we haven't collected all the moonlight we need yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How vexing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:52.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us exterminate the intruders before Reitei-sama hears of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the moon's true form appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:02.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them survive if they've seen Deliora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must put intruders to sleep for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.78,0:21:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words... love!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, death?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why don't we catch 'em and make 'em answer questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:25.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet. Let's look around a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:28.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotten kind of complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:31.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this "Reitei-sama" person?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:35.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did they bring Deliora here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:39.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And how did they find the place it was sealed anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The place it was sealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:45.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This thing was sealed in a glacier on the northern continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An immortal demon that ran rampant ten years ago in the land of Isvan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The demon who Ul, the wizard who taught me magic, gave her life to seal away! {I originally wrote "risked" too, but had to go back and change it when I learned what actually happened}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what connection it has to the curse on this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but this thing should never be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this Reitei person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna let you get away with throwing dirt on Ul's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away to someplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride on a tin horse, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:44.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad that my beloved doll can't talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.43,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:51.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think of you tears start to flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:56.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a crybaby, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,In the moon (the moon) at night (at night)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always (I'm always)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:04.50,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,searching for the rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:07.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so much it's like I'm under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This love is a monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,from which I'll never awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.34,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've completely fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:23.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what spell I could chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:29.51,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting this and that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love you like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:39.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I want to be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"You got me."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:45.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:59.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, have you heard of this Moon Drip?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:00.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:04.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know, but it says it's something about drips from the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:05.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, could it be food?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.64,0:24:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.40,0:24:07.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be candies!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.93,0:24:10.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They make them by concentrating moon juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.43,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.77,0:24:16.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Moon Drip!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:19.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how do you squeeze out moon juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.01,0:24:20.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to wait for the next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.81,0:24:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha! I can't wait for these Moon Drops!
